      "cooked": "<p>Nuk e di nese eshte e vertete apo jo, nese ndonje nga ju mund ta konfermoje/hedh poshte vertetesine e ketij dokumenti</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/3/3a00e3fb57f067c41f008ce2297340ccb874464a.jpg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/3a00e3fb57f067c41f008ce2297340ccb874464a\" title=\"karuci.jpg\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/3/3a00e3fb57f067c41f008ce2297340ccb874464a.jpg\" alt=\"karuci\" width=\"620\" height=\"800\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/3/3a00e3fb57f067c41f008ce2297340ccb874464a_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">karuci.jpg</span><span class=\"informations\">744×960 93.8 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Lolita16112015/photos/a.1497531483881615.1073741829.1496781900623240/1743718155929612/?type=3&amp;theater\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Burimi</a></p>",
