      "created_at": "2017-09-15T14:09:48.117Z",
      "cooked": "<p>ciklikja <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/smile.png?v=5\" title=\":smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":smile:\">  po ta shofesh mire eshte ne fakt nje spirale…<br>\nSpiralja e progresit!</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
      "like_count": 0
